Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,There was a time when a meteor flashing through the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:57.96,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,struck man with a deep sense of wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.94,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Even today man's reaction to a meteoric display
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:09.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,is likely to jam the switchboards with reports of imminent invasion from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:16.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But as heirs to the knowledge disciplines and apparatus of the Scientific Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:21.05,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,we are familiar with and at least partially understand the meteoric phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:27.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A meteoroid traveling in space outside our atmosphere remains unseen by man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,while the molecules in space are so dispersed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:34.04,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A collision with them causes no visible effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:40.02,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,If its trajectory traverses the Earth's atmosphere, it becomes a meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:44.49,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Here it begins to collide with more molecules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:47.68,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,These collisions become more and more frequent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:53.50,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,as the meteor descends into the denser air of lower altitude, causing it to decelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:57.93,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Each collision worth some of the energy of motion into heat energy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,and the heat continues to increase
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,until the meteor itself becomes incandescent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.35,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,scribing it's visible path through the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:12.13,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Destroyed in the atmosphere by this heating, most meteors present no danger to man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.03,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Now and then one is large enough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,to survive its passage through the atmosphere to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:23.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,It is then called a meteorite and some are very large indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:29.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Peter Parameter became interested in meteors early in his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:31.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And once wrote a paper titled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A thermal kinetic description of bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.83,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,and passage through a plastic medium of nonlinear density
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.33,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,at random velocities and angles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,which could be just about summed up with this equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:43.99,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,With this equation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.82,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,is fellow scientists and designers are able to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:50.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,the effects of atmospheric penetration on differing bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:54.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Those with different ballistic coefficients at various velocities and angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:59.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For example, if two bodies of different weights enter the Earth's atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,with the same velocity and entry angle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:06.89,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,both the heavy body and the light one will begin to heat up at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,What impacts of air molecules slow the light body sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:17.44,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This deceleration of the light body occurs at higher altitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.64,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,while the heavier more energetic body penetrates deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,before it reaches peak deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The total amount of heat generated by the lighter one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.97,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,is less than that generated by the heavy one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.83,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,whose larger mass is it greater kinetic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.64,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Two identical bodies with the same velocity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:41.16,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,entering the atmosphere at different angles also will decelerate at different rates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.51,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The steeper angle causes a more rapid encounter with the dense air
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,resulting in more abrupt deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The total heat generated will be the same for both bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,but peak heating will be less for the shallow entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:04:01.42,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,With identical meteors entering at the same angle but with different velocities,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:05.28,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,the faster meteor under heavier bombardment by air molecules
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:10.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,will have greater deceleration generating more heat and at a higher rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But Dr. Parameter is no longer merely an observer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.59,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,interested in understanding the phenomena of meteors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.32,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A meteor is just an aimless traveler in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:29.63,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Doc finds himself now involved in designs with a purpose and an aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.50,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A missile has a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:36.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And a spacecraft has a destination, a journey's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,To these Doc applies his knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:45.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He knows natural phenomena both of aimless meteor and aimed missile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.00,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He knows that as they traverse the atmosphere they heat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:54.28,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,If the heating or deceleration of a vehicle is excessive the mission is threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.73,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Man cannot change the laws of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,So he must use his knowledge to work within those laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.87,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter knows that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:08.29,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,the two natural enemies to successful atmospheric penetration
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.02,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,are deceleration and heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.66,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He can fight these enemies on two possible fronts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:21.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,First on the design front by modifying the vehicle shape and size relative to its weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.31,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,In other words its ballistic coefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.64,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And second on the program front,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,by altering the vehicles trajectory,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:35.22,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,its velocity, its attitude and its angle of entry into the Earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.84,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter is now ready to use his technology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:43.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,to plan a successful re-entry for an ICBM warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:47.77,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He knows that of the two natural enemies, deceleration and heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,High deceleration is not a problem with a warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,but too much heat could destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:58.49,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He first surveys the project on the program front.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:04.87,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He knows that the re-entry velocities and angles are essentially set by the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.37,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But to reduce heat load, the velocity of the re-entry vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.77,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,could theoretically be reduced by firing a retro rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.71,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,On investigation he finds that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:19.38,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,in order to decrease for re-entry velocity sufficiently by this method,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.13,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,a retro thrust system would be required
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,weighing many times the weight of the warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.44,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This method is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.29,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He next considers the possibility of changing the re-entry angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:35.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He knows that a shallow angle will lessen the peak heat load
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,by stretching the heating over a longer period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:42.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But the total heat generated will be the same either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.61,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And the vehicle could absorb even more heat during this longer re-entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:51.51,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, a shallow re-entry angle has other serious drawbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:56.86,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,First a shallow angle impairs accuracy by deflection in the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:02.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Second, it affords more time for enemy interception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.47,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A steep re-entry improves the missiles chances of avoiding interception
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.83,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,and of reaching its target with minimum atmospheric deflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:17.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,In this case or during the program is not the answer to the heat problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:23.00,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter must attack the problem of heat on the design front.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:29.47,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Logic would seem to indicate that fast travel requires a streamlined shape
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,to slice its way through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,At subsonic velocities this is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But at supersonic speeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:40.59,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,a moving vehicle displaces air molecules which bounced off, forming a shockwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:46.51,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,As speed increases the shock wave becomes more severe and heating increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:54.63,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,An ICBM will have a free-fall re-entry speed in excess of 23,000 feet per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:08:00.42,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,At this speed, the heat of molecular collision and friction, shearing of air molecules
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:05.61,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,is concentrated in a narrow zone along the surface of a streamlined vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:11.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The heat generated may cause the temperature to exceed 15000 degrees Fahrenheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,To combat this terrific heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:22.35,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter designs instead a re-entry vehicle with a blunt frontal area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The blunt shape creates its shockwave somewhat ahead of the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This occurs because the atmospheric molecules
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,colliding with its frontal surface bounce back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.71,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And intercept others coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.94,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Setting up a kind of picket line in advance of the warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:48.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The peak heat is generated in this area away from the surface of the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:51.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Although the blunt shape
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:55.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,decreases the peak heating of the warhead to half that of a streamline shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.39,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,it will still heat up to 7,000 degrees Fahrenheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.96,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Much too hot for unprotected warhead structures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,To further reduce heating,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.06,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter must find other techniques in addition to the blunt shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.68,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,His first solution is the heatsink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.76,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Use the blunt design and add a mass of heat conducting metal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,large enough to absorb most of the heat generated during re-entry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.97,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,without melting before impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.31,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,It works, but he is not yet satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The weight of the heatsink displaces more than one-fourth of the payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Furthermore the blunt designs slows the missile,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.75,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,keeping it in the atmosphere a longer time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:40.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,making it less accurate and easier to intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For the greatest accuracy and shortest time in the atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.89,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Doc knows that the streamline shape is the best
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:53.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,but the heatsink cannot absorb and distribute the sudden extremely
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.97,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,generated during the re-entry of a streamlined vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:07.19,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Doc reasons, {\i1}if the heat cannot be absorbed why not eject it as fast as it's generated?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.06,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The answer is ablation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:11.93,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ablation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Coat the frontal surface of the streamline missile
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.89,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,with layers of a blade of material composed of fibres resins and ceramics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:25.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This ablative coating protects the missile from the extreme heat in several ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.07,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,It is a poor heat conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Its surface gradually melts away taking heat with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:35.66,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And it's vapor forms a thin insulating layer deflecting some of the heat from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.99,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The ablative principle combats the heat problem effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:44.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,and permits steeper re-entry angles while adding a minimum of weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:47.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The streamlined missile with its increased speed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:52.04,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,affords the least possibility of interception and the greatest accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:57.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,It does produce a huge deceleration factor approaching 150 G's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.67,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Fortunately this poses no threat to a warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:07.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But for manned or other recovery missions, the G load is a most important factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:12.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For manned re-entry this force should be held below 10 G's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:17.33,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A shallow re-entry angle of about 1 to 5 degrees is the simple answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The shallower the angle, the less the G load.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But this will be sustained over a longer period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:28.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This means a longer time at high speed through the friction of the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:32.62,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Let's take a moment to see why this is not desirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:35.49,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.86,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A gentleman we have here a kettle of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.32,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Heathcliff, we can use you in this experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Oh boy an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Thank you sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Now if we may have another kettle of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.60,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And you're stand-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:54.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.25,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Now we'll proceed with the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:58.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,We'll add the same amount of fuel under each kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.10,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But alter the form of the fuel under one kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.00,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,To make it burn faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,We ignite both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.30,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And compare the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.30,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:25.30,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,I'd like to point out that the fast burning fuel although reaching its intensity quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Exhausted itself quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.67,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The heat absorbed was negligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:34.16,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The slow burning fuel on the other hand gradually increases its intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,It will generate the same total heat load
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,but over a longer period of time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,and you'll notice more heat is absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.15,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Thank you Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Thank you Dr. Parameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.50,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,So although the peak heat generated in the shallow re-entry is less,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.02,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,the capsule is in the heating regime for a longer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:02.38,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And without the utmost protection would absorb an intolerable amount of heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:07.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For manned re-entry, Dr. Parameter overcomes the deceleration enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,through program with the shallow angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:12.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But he must combat heat on the design front.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:17.05,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A blunt shape to cause a detached shock wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.62,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A picket line against heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And ablative materials for additional heat control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.65,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The doc is confident his new design will fulfill the requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Now to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:35.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He wants low peak deceleration so the shallow re-entry path is mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:39.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This brings him down safely if a little off target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.84,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,To achieve some control and accuracy as well as safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.44,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter has been working on other design concepts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.87,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,particularly shapes that produce lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He knows that a ballistic missile is designed and programmed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.76,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,to hit a particular point on the Earth's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,A manned ballistic vehicle with the same objective
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:06.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,is much less accurate due to its design and long shallow penetration
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,but a lifting vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:12.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,which is capable of descending at a still more shallow angle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:16.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,and with an extremely low deceleration rate is able to change direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:23.03,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This control gives it wide selectivity of landing sites within a large footprint area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For the shortest range within the footprint,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:32.05,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,the vehicle is pulled up into a maximum lift attitude at re-entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:37.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,This induces maximum drag, causing a steeper, more abrupt descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.68,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For the longest possible range,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:45.34,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,the vehicle must assume the attitude of maximum lift / drag ratio
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:51.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,this footprint huge at first shrinks gradually as the vehicle descends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:56.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter while considering the advantages of lifting vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,is also aware of their drawbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:01.85,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,First the lifting structure itself imposes weight penalties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,which compete with the all-important matter of payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:10.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Then lifting vehicles may also spend up to 20 minutes in the heat regime
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:15.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,and being more streamlined they require a still more complex heat protection system
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,competing still further with payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:25.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter with his associates has studied the strategy of atmospheric penetration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.67,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He knows it's natural enemies, deceleration and heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And has met them on the two fronts of program and design.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.94,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He has accomplished important objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.71,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For the intercontinental ballistic missile,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:47.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,the objectives are rapid atmospheric penetration and accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:52.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The warheads natural enemy is sudden intense heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:58.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Its program high velocity, steep re-entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:04.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Its design streamlined with ablation to combat sudden heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:09.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,For a manned or other recovery mission the objectives are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:12.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,first of all safety and then control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:17.75,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The mission's natural enemies, high deceleration sustained Heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:22.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Its program shallow re-entry for low deceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The vehicles design blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:29.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Yet with control capabilities, a maneuverable lifting shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:35.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,The resulting long duration within the heat regime exacts a weight penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.62,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Because a complex heat protection system is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,There will always be problems to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:48.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Dr. Parameter has worked out successful compromises so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:51.60,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But he is still puzzling, still exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.16,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He plucks his graphs, his curves and flings them boldly into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,But he knows we have barely gotten our little toe into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,And he constantly seeks to improve that toe hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He must hold to the possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Yet he constantly works along its impossible edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:15.73,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,He has opened the way for man's safe re-entry into the Earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-Bold-33,,0,0,0,,Journey's end for space travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,曾几何时 一颗流星在天空中闪烁的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:57.96,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,击中人惊叹浓浓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.94,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,即使在今天 人的反应到大气显示器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:09.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,可能是从太空入侵迫在眉睫的报告 以堵塞交换机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:16.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但是作为继承人科学革命的学科知识和设备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:21.05,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,我们所熟悉的 并且至少部分理解的流星现象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:27.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,流星在大气层以外的太空旅游仍然是看不见的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而在空间中的分子如此分散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:34.04,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,与之碰撞产生没有明显的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:40.02,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,如果它的轨道穿过地球大气层 成为一颗流星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:44.49,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这始于多种分子碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:47.68,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这些碰撞越来越频繁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:53.50,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,作为流星下降到较低的高度的更致密的空气 使其减速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:57.93,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,每一次碰撞值得一些运动的能量转化为热能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,和热继续增加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,直到流星本身成为白炽灯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.35,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,通过夜空划出它的可见路径
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:12.13,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,在此加热大气层破坏 大多数流星一种不会危及人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.03,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,现在再一个足够大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,穿过大气层到地球生存的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:23.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,然后 它被称为陨石 有些是确实很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:29.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,彼得参数医生产生了兴趣 流星在他的职业生涯的早期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:31.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而曾经写过一篇题为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,机构的热动力学描述
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.83,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,并通过非线性密度的塑料介质通道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.33,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,在随机速度和角度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这可能大约只是概括了这个公式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:43.99,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,有了这个公式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.82,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,是其他科学家和设计师们能够解释
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:50.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,大气渗透对不同机构的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:54.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,那些在各种速度和角度不同的弹道系数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:59.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,例如 如果不同的权重的两个机构进入地球大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,以相同的速度和进入角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:06.89,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,两个重体和所述光的一个将开始的同时升温
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,什么空气分子的影响慢光体越快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:17.44,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,光体的该减速发生在更高的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.64,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而较重的更有活力的身体更深地渗透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,之前达到峰值减速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,的热由打火机一个产生的总量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.97,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,小于由重之一生成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.83,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,其较大的肿块是更大的动能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.64,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,以相同的速度两个相同的机构
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:41.16,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,在不同的角度进入大气层也将减速以不同的速率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.51,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,该更陡的角度导致与稠密的空气更加快速遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,从而导致更多的突然减速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,所产生的总热量将是这两个机构同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但峰值加热会少了浅条目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:04:01.42,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,具有相同流星以相同的角度但以不同的速度进入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:05.28,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,由空气分子下较重轰击越快流星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:10.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,将有更大的减速产生更多的热量 并以较高的速率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但是参数博士已不再仅仅是一个观察者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.59,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,有兴趣了解的流星现象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.32,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,流星只是在太空漫无目的的旅客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:29.63,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,文件发现自己现在从事有目的和目标设计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.50,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,导弹有一个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:36.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而航天器都有一个目标 一个旅程的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这些文件适用于他的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:45.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他知道这两个漫无目的的流星导弹瞄准的自然现象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.00,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他知道 当它们穿过大气层 他们热了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:54.28,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,如果车辆的加热或减速是过度的使命受到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.73,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,人不能改变自然规律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,所以他必须在这些法律中使用自己的知识来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.87,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数医生知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:08.29,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,两大天敌成功大气渗透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.02,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,是减速和热量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.66,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他可以在两种可能的战线对抗这些敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:21.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,首先在设计前通过修改车辆的形状和相对尺寸以它的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.31,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,换言之其弹道系数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.64,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,其次在该程序前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,通过改变车辆轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:35.22,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,它的速度 它的态度和它进入地球大气层的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.84,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士现在已经可以使用他的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:43.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,策划一个成功的再进入一个洲际弹道导弹弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:47.77,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他知道 这两个天敌 减速和热量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,高减速是不带核弹头的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但过多的热量会破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:58.49,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他首先调查的程序前面的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:04.87,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他知道 再入速度和角度基本上是由任务设置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.37,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但是 以减少热负荷 在再入大气层飞行器的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.77,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,理论上可以发射了火箭复古减少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.71,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,经调查 他发现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:19.38,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,为了充分地利用该方法以减少重新进入速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.13,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,复古的推力系统 将需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,称重多次弹头的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.44,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这种方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.29,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他接着考虑改变再入角的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:35.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他知道 一个小的角度将减少高峰负荷热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,通过在较长的时间周期拉伸的加热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:42.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但产生的总热量是相同的两种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.61,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而车辆会这样长再入过程中吸收更多的热量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:51.51,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,此外 浅再入角有其他严重缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:56.86,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,第一浅角度也妨碍精度由大气中的偏转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:02.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,其次 它可以提供敌方拦截更多的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.47,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,陡峭的再入提高避免拦截导弹机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.83,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,并以最小的大气偏转达到其目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:17.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下 或者在节目中是没有答案的散热问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:23.00,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士见缝插针在设计前的热问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:29.47,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,逻辑似乎表明 迅游需要流线型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,通过空气切片的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,在亚音速的速度 这是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但在超音速的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:40.59,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,移动的车辆位移空气分子 其弹开 形成了冲击波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:46.51,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,随着速度的增加冲击波变得更加严重和加热增大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:54.63,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,洲际弹道导弹将有超过每秒23000英尺自由落体再入速度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:08:00.42,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,在此速度下 分子碰撞和摩擦热 剪切空气分子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:05.61,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,集中在沿流线型车辆的表面上的狭窄区域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:11.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,所产生的热量可能导致温度超过15000华氏度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,为了解决这个酷热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:22.35,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士设计 而不是用钝器正面面积的再入飞行器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,钝形创建其冲击波有些车辆前方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这是因为大气分子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,以其前表面反弹碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.71,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,和截距别人进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.94,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,提前弹头建立一种纠察线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:48.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,峰热量在从车辆的表面这个区域远离生成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:51.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,虽然钝形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:55.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,减小该流线形的弹头的一半的峰值加热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.39,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,它仍然会升温到7000华氏度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.96,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,太热未受保护的弹头结构
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,为了进一步降低加热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.06,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士必须找到除了钝形的其他技术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.68,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他的第一个解决方案是散热器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.76,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,使用生硬设计 并添加导热金属的质量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,大到足以吸收大部分再入大气层时产生的热量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.97,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,无冲击前融化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.31,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,它的工作原理 但他没有得到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,散热器位移多于四分之一有效载荷的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,此外 钝设计减慢导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.75,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,保持它在空气中较长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:40.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,使得它不太准确 更容易拦截
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,对于在大气中的最大精度和最短的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.89,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,督知道 流线造型是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:53.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但是散热器不能吸收和分配非常突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.97,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,一个精简车辆的重新进入过程中产生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:07.19,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,文件的原因 如果这些热量不能被吸收 为什么没有那么快 因为它产生的弹出？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.06,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,答案是消融
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:11.93,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,消融
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,大衣流线型导弹的前表面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.89,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,与纤维树脂和陶瓷组成的材料的叶片的层
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:25.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这种烧蚀涂层保护从极热在几个方面的导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.07,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这是一种不良的热导体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,它的表面逐渐融化吸收热量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:35.66,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,和它的蒸气形成薄的绝缘层偏转一些来自表面的热量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.99,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,烧蚀性原则能够有效消除散热问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:44.20,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,和同时加入的最小重量的许可证更陡的再入角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:47.69,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,流线型导弹其增加的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:52.04,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,得到拦截的可能性最小和最大的精度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:57.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,它产生接近150 G公司的一个巨大的减速因素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.67,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,好在这种情况对弹头的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:07.08,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但对于载人或其它救援任务时 克负荷是一个最重要的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:12.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,对于载人再入这支部队应保持低于10个G的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:17.33,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,大约1至5度的浅再入角是简单的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,较浅角度 较少的克负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但是 这将在一段较长时间持续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:28.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这意味着在高速穿过大气层的摩擦更长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:32.62,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,让我们花点时间来看看为什么这是不可取的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.72,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:35.49,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.86,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,绅士我们这里有水的水壶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.32,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,希刺克厉夫 我们可以在这个实验中使用你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,哦 孩子的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,现在 如果我们可以有另一个水水壶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.60,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而你是替身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:54.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.25,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,现在 我们将与实验继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:58.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.74,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,我们将每个锅下添加燃料的量相同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.10,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但改变下一个水壶燃料的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.00,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,为了使它燃烧得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.78,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,我们同时点燃两个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.30,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,并比较结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.30,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:25.30,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,我想指出的是 快速燃烧的燃料 虽然很快达到其强度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,很快耗尽本身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.67,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,吸收的热量可以忽略不计
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:34.16,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,在另一方面 缓慢燃烧的燃料逐渐增加其强度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这将产生相同的总热负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但在一段较长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,你会发现更多的热量被吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.15,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,谢谢希刺克厉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.12,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,谢谢医生的参数
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.50,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,因此 尽管在浅再入产生的峰值热量少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.02,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,胶囊是在更长的时间加热制度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:02.38,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而如果没有最大限度保护将吸收的热量无法忍受的量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:07.52,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,对于载人再入参数博士克服减速敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.91,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,通过与浅角度程序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:12.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但他必须在设计前打击热量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:17.05,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,钝形状以使分离的冲击波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.62,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,对热纠察线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,和烧蚀材料的额外热量的控制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.65,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,该文档是自信的他的新设计将满足要求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.58,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,现在尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:35.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他希望低峰减速使浅重新进入路径是强制性的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:39.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,如果稍微偏离目标这使他失望安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.84,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,为了实现一定的控制和精确度以及安全性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.44,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士一直致力于研究其他的设计理念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.87,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,特别形状的产生升力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他知道 弹道导弹的设计和编程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.76,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,击中地球表面上的特定点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.18,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,载人弹道车辆具有相同的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:06.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,是准确的要少得多 因为它的设计和长的浅穿透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但提升车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:12.21,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,其能够下降的在更浅的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:16.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,并具有极低的减速率是能够改变方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:23.03,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这种控制给它一个大的占位面积内的着陆点的宽泛的选择性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,对于覆盖范围内最短的范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:32.05,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,车辆被拉成在再入最大升程的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:37.24,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这导致最大的阻力 造成一个陡峭的 更陡峭的斜坡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.68,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,为了尽可能长的范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:45.34,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,车辆必须承担最大升力/阻力比的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:51.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这个足迹第一次收缩逐渐车辆下降很大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:56.01,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士同时考虑起重车的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,也意识到自己的缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:01.85,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,一是提升结构本身重量施加处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.95,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,与有效载荷的所有重要事项竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:10.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,然后提升车辆也可能会花长达20分钟的热政权
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:15.54,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,而被更精简 他们需要一个更复杂的热保护系统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.27,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,竞争还在进一步有效载荷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:25.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,参数博士和他的同事研究了大气渗透的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.67,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他知道它的天敌 减速和热量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,并满足他们在计划和设计的两条战线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.94,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他已经完成了重要的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.71,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,对于洲际弹道导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:47.88,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,目标是快速渗透大气和准确性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:52.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,该弹头天敌是突如其来的酷暑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:58.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,其方案高速度 陡峭的再入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:04.26,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,它的设计与流线型消融打击骤热
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:09.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,对于载人或其它救援任务的目标是：
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:12.92,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,首先安全 然后控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:17.75,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,特派团的天敌 高减速持续的热量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:22.56,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,其方案浅再入低减速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.40,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,这些车辆设计生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:29.57,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,然而 随着控制功能 可调遣提升形状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:35.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,热状态内将得到的长的持续时间苛求的重量损失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.62,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,由于复杂的热保护系统是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.80,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,总会有问题需要解决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:48.09,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,到目前为止参数博士已经摸索出成功的妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:51.60,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但他仍然是令人费解的 仍在探索中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.16,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,拨弄着曲线图 他的曲线和大胆地甩它们送入太空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.41,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,但他知道 我们几乎没有得到我们的小脚趾送入太空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:04.48,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他不断寻求改善该脚趾保持
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.46,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他必须坚持的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.14,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,然而 他不断地沿着它不可能边工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:15.73,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,他开辟了人类的安全重新进入地球大气层的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.53,720P-sorc-hans-sans-medi-50,,0,0,0,,旅程的终点​​为太空旅行
